        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Linux Web Console]]></title>
            <link>https://abhilashreddysh.github.io/wiki/blog/linuxwebconsole</link>
            <guid>https://abhilashreddysh.github.io/wiki/blog/linuxwebconsole</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Version - 1.0]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Web page setup to moniter services and stats of a remote linux machine</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info alert alert--info admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>Version - 1.0</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p><a href="https://github.com/abhilashreddysh/AutomationScripts/tree/main/WebConsole" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Repository Link</a></p></div></div><h3 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_WYt5" id="requirements">Requirements<a href="#requirements" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Requirements" title="Direct link to Requirements">​</a></h3><ul><li>Nginx</li><li>PHP</li></ul><h3 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_WYt5" id="setup">Setup<a href="#setup" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Setup" title="Direct link to Setup">​</a></h3><ul><li>Download the folder and save in nginx <code>sites-enabled</code> folder.</li><li>Point the default nginx webpage to this folder.</li><li>To be able to use the restart feature allow <code>www-data</code> user to act as sudo for these commands</li></ul><div class="language-config codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockTitle_Ktv7">/etc/sudoers.d/www-data-access</div><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-config codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">%www-data ALL=NOPASSWD: /bin/systemctl restart nginx</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">%www-data ALL=NOPASSWD: /bin/systemctl restart sshd</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">%www-data ALL=NOPASSWD: /bin/systemctl restart smbd</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">%www-data ALL=NOPASSWD: /bin/systemctl restart transmission-daemon</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div><p>This will allow www-data user to be able to use only the above commands as a sudo user.</p><p>Add more if there are any other services to be monitered.</p>]]></content:encoded>
            <author>abhilashreddysh.99@gmail.com (Abhilash Reddy)</author>
            <category>linux</category>
            <category>bash</category>
            <category>php</category>
            <category>moniter</category>
            <category>web</category>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Linux Status Mail]]></title>
            <link>https://abhilashreddysh.github.io/wiki/blog/linuxpythonmail</link>
            <guid>https://abhilashreddysh.github.io/wiki/blog/linuxpythonmail</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 25 May 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Version - 1.3]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Python Script to get linux services update through mail. Can be automated and scheduled to run in time intervals using crontab.</p><div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info alert alert--info admonition_LlT9"><div class="admonitionHeading_tbUL"><span class="admonitionIcon_kALy"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>Version - 1.3</div><div class="admonitionContent_S0QG"><p><a href="https://github.com/abhilashreddysh/AutomationScripts/tree/main/LinuxStatusMail" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Repository Link</a></p></div></div><h3 class="anchor anchorWithHideOnScrollNavbar_WYt5" id="setup">Setup<a href="#setup" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Setup" title="Direct link to Setup">​</a></h3><p>You can use the <code>generateConfig.py</code> to generate a config file by providing the required inputs for the first time and later update the generated config file accordingly.</p><p>To do it manually create the below file in the project root dir</p><div class="language-config codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#F8F8F2;--prism-background-color:#282A36"><div class="codeBlockTitle_Ktv7">config.py -- (Generated from generateconfig.py)</div><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-config codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">gmailUser = &lt;Sender Email&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">gmailPassword = &lt;Password&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">recipient = &lt;Recipients Mail&gt;</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#F8F8F2"><span class="token plain">services_to_be_monitered = &lt;List of Services to be monitered&gt;</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
            <author>abhilashreddysh.99@gmail.com (Abhilash Reddy)</author>
